'''Peter Bagge''' (born [[December 11]], [[1950s|1957]]) is an American [[Star Wars comic books|comics]] artist who wrote and penciled the comics "[[Failing Up With Jar Jar Binks]]" and "[[Nobody's Perfect]]" for [[Star Wars Tales]].

